Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	10:01:04 PM	03:53:02	APAC_PH_Manila_7th Floor_Recption Door 1-701	OutDirection	Out of office	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	10:02:19 PM	00:01:15	APAC_PH_Manila_6th Floor_Entry Door 2	InDirection	Red Zone	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	10:08:06 PM	00:05:47	APAC_PH_Manila_6th Floor Enrty Door 1	OutDirection	Out of office	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	10:09:13 PM	00:01:07	APAC_PH_Manila_7th Floor_Recption Door 2-701	InDirection	Red Zone	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	10:36:37 PM	00:27:24	APAC_PH_Manila_7th Floor_Recption Door 1-701	OutDirection	Out of office	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	10:37:20 PM	00:00:43	APAC_PH_Manila_6th Floor_Entry Door 2	InDirection	Red Zone	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	11:14:51 PM	00:37:31	APAC_PH_Manila_6th Floor Enrty Door 1	OutDirection	Out of office	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	04-12-2025	11:15:40 PM	00:00:49	APAC_PH_Manila_7th Floor_Recption Door 2-701	InDirection	Red Zone	
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	05-12-2025	12:52:46 AM	00:00:00	APAC_PH_Manila_7th Floor_Recption Door 1-701	OutDirection	Out of office	4th Dec Shift End here 
Beduria, Reshellyn Baroca	323630	608269	05-12-2025	5:53:08 AM	05:00:22	APAC_PH_Manila_7th Floor_Recption Door 2-701	InDirection	Red Zone	5th Dec Shift Start here
